main.java.gui

Class QualityRulesResultFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.gui.QualityRulesResultFrame

  • public class QualityRulesResultFrame
extends java.lang.Object
    The Code Quality Rules Results Frame will display a table with the results for running the CodeQualityRules against the methods data uploaded by the user.
